cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper deals with the formalisation of conceptual data modelling languages and the development of logic profiles for them. This involves aspects of database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the need for interoperability and tooling support, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper mentions the use of Description Logics (DL), which is a subfield of programming languages (cs.PL).
